{"title":"New HANDUP Gloves Pro model helps Neko Mulally get a grip","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/23/handup-pro-performance-glove/","date":1632398434000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><main><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120005/HANDUP-FEATURE-IMAGE-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"HANDUP Pro Performance Glove - lifestyle image\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120005/HANDUP-FEATURE-IMAGE-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120005/HANDUP-FEATURE-IMAGE-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120005/HANDUP-FEATURE-IMAGE-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120005/HANDUP-FEATURE-IMAGE-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120005/HANDUP-FEATURE-IMAGE.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></main><main role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-272439\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>The last thing a serious MTBer needs is a questionable grip on the bars. Yet, the more extreme your offroad cycling gets, the less likely your old gear will be up for the chore. That’s why sports outfitter HANDUP partnered with two-time National Downhill champ <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2015/02/05/bike-check-neko-mulallys-new-scott-gambler-w-prototype-fox-shock/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Neko Mulally</a> to refine a racing glove that could pull out all the stops.</p><h3>HANDUP Pro Performance Glove</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120012/handup-prop-perf-alm-detail-e1632326665383.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120012/handup-prop-perf-alm-detail-e1632326665383.jpg\" alt=\"HANDUP Pro Performance Glove - palm detail. All images c. HANDUP\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\"></a></p><p>Meet the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/06/handup-pbr-collection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HANDUP</a> Pro Performance Glove. The Pro Performance comes with all the usual tenets — full-touchscreen capability, a built-in sweat cloth, ventilation. But it’s the glove’s big-league design improvements that set it apart from past Handup models.</p><blockquote data-instgrm-captioned=\"\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CUDEg7oF3-D/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" data-instgrm-version=\"13\" id=\"instagram-media-payload-0\"></blockquote><h3>Pro Performance Features</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120018/handup-prop-perf-upper.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120018/handup-prop-perf-upper.jpg\" alt=\"HANDUP Pro Performance Glove - wrist detail. All images c. HANDUP\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120018/handup-prop-perf-upper.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120018/handup-prop-perf-upper-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120018/handup-prop-perf-upper-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120018/handup-prop-perf-upper-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120018/handup-prop-perf-upper-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><ul><li>Breathable Clarino leather palm</li><li>Compression-molded, slip-on neoprene cuff</li><li>Full-touch smart device functionality</li><li>Integrated sweat cloth</li><li>Laser-cut ventilation</li><li>LITE mesh fourchette finger webbing</li><li>LITE silicone fingertip and palm grips</li><li>Rolled fingertip construction</li><li>Smooth-stretch upper</li></ul><h3>Pricing, Availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120015/handup-prop-erf-fingertips.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120015/handup-prop-erf-fingertips.jpg\" alt=\"HANDUP Pro Performance Glove - fingertip detailAll images c. HANDUP\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120015/handup-prop-erf-fingertips.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120015/handup-prop-erf-fingertips-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120015/handup-prop-erf-fingertips-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120015/handup-prop-erf-fingertips-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/22120015/handup-prop-erf-fingertips-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>HANDUP launched the unisex Pro Performance Glove ($36 MSRP) this week, which it offers in sizes XXS-XXL and black camo or white camo colorways.</p><p>Wipe those sweaty palms off and click over to <a href=\"https://handupgloves.com/collections/new-releases/products/pro-glove-white-camo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HANDUP.com</a> to grab a pair.</p></section></article></main></div></div>","author":"Jilli Cluff","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"b6182612af3